'''Booking Holdings'''（{{nasdaq|BKNG}}），透過該集團旗下六個品牌：[[缤客|缤客]]、Priceline.com、[[雅高达|雅高達]]、[[客涯|客涯]]、rentalcars.com以及OpenTable， 提供消費者與當地廠商旅遊相關服務的線上供應商。Booking Holdings在總共超過200個以上的國家營運，並支援美洲、歐洲、亞洲、中東地區等超過40種語言。

Booking Holdings的前身是Priceline集團，到2018年二月正式改名。<ref name=公司更名為Booking>{{cite web|url=https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/the-priceline-group-inc-nasdaq-pcln-announces-name-change-to-booking-holdings-inc-300601628.html|title=The Priceline Group Inc. Announces Name Change to Booking Holdings Inc.|publisher=PR Newswire|accessdate=2018-03-04|archive-date=2018-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180228223422/https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/the-priceline-group-inc-nasdaq-pcln-announces-name-change-to-booking-holdings-inc-300601628.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 歷史 ==
1997年，Priceline.com透過「Name Your Own Price 」的競標模式開始旅遊網站。1999年，Priceline集團進行了IPO，首日便募得了129億的市值，為歷史上最高紀錄。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.pricelinegroup.com/about/history/|title=History|accessdate=6 July 2016|website=The Priceline Group, Inc.|archive-date=2017-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170619192714/http://www.pricelinegroup.com/about/history/}}</ref> 同年，他們嘗試用同樣的競標模式銷售如雜貨、里程、房地產等產品與服務，不過隔年便停止此項業務。2002年，Jeff Boyd被指名為CEO，直到2013年才轉任董事会主席。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/priceline-jeff-boyd-2012-1|title=Jeff Boyd|accessdate=24 December 2014|website=Business Insider|archive-date=2021-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301151104/http://www.businessinsider.com/priceline-jeff-boyd-2012-1}}</ref>

2014年四月，Priceline.com 股份有限公司更名为Priceline集團，以呼應公司以旗下獨立的各品牌。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.businessweek.com/articles/2014-04-01/why-priceline-needed-a-new-name|title=Why Priceline Needed a New Name|accessdate=26 December 2014|website=Business Week|archive-date=2015-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150126021625/http://www.businessweek.com/articles/2014-04-01/why-priceline-needed-a-new-name}}</ref> 2014年，Darren Huston接任Jeff Boyd，被指名為Priceline集團之執行長。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://investing.businessweek.com/research/stocks/people/person.asp?personId=754957&ticker=MSFT&previousCapId=27536&previousTitle=DEVRY%20INC|title=Darren R. Huston|accessdate=26 December 2014|website=Investing Business Week}}</ref>2016年四月Jeff Boyd回报Priceline集團之執行長。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/priceline-group-ceo-darren-huston-resigns-chairman-jeffery-h-boyd-appointed-interim-ceo-300259053.html|title=Priceline Group CEO Darren Huston Resigns; Chairman Jeffery H. Boyd Appointed Interim CEO|publisher=The Priceline Group,Inc.|accessdate=2016-04-29|archive-date=2019-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190827130229/https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/priceline-group-ceo-darren-huston-resigns-chairman-jeffery-h-boyd-appointed-interim-ceo-300259053.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2018年2月22日全球最大的在線旅遊集團Priceline Group宣布，公司更名為Booking Holdings Inc。更名後，公司總部將繼續留在美國康涅狄格州的Norwalk。公司股票代碼將更換為“BKNG”，2月27日生效。<ref name=公司更名為Booking/>

== 併購 ==
2004年，Priceline.com透過收購Travelwen以及Active Hotels的主要股權進入了飯店零售領域。2005年，Priceline集團收購Booking.com（缤客）並將之與Active Hotels合併。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.tnooz.com/article/why-pricelines-purchase-of-booking-com-was-the-most-profitable-travel-deal-of-the-2000s/|title=Why Priceline's Purchase of Booking.com Was the Most Profitable Deal of the 2000's|accessdate=24 December 2014|website=Tnooz|archive-date=2018-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180722011655/https://www.tnooz.com/article/why-pricelines-purchase-of-booking-com-was-the-most-profitable-travel-deal-of-the-2000s/}}</ref>Priceline集團於2007年收購[[雅高达|雅高達]]。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/11/08/idUSIN20071108160105PCLN20071108|title=Priceline.com Acquires Asian Online Hotel Reservation Service Company Agoda|accessdate=24 December 2014|website=Reuters.com|archive-date=2015-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151109162258/http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/11/08/idUSIN20071108160105PCLN20071108}}</ref> 2010年，他們收購跨國汽車租賃服務商TravelJigsaw（今為rentalcars.com）<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.tnooz.com/article/priceline-acquires-car-rental-firm-traveljigsaw-as-part-of-expansion-drive/|title=Priceline Acquire Car Rental Firm Travel Jigsaw As Part of Expansion Drive|accessdate=24 December 2014|website=Tnooz|archive-date=2018-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180926041057/https://www.tnooz.com/article/priceline-acquires-car-rental-firm-traveljigsaw-as-part-of-expansion-drive/}}</ref> 而KAYAK則是於2013年被收購。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://video.cnbc.com/gallery/?video=3000128132|title=Priceline Snaps Up Kayak for 1.8 Billion|accessdate=24 December 2014|website=CNBC.com|archive-date=2016-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160621163521/http://video.cnbc.com/gallery/?video=3000128132}}</ref> 2014年，Priceline集團以26億的現金收購了OpenTable。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/samanthasharf/2014/06/13/priceline-reserves-opentable-for-2-6-billion|title=Priceline Reserves OpenTable for 2.6 Billion|website=Forbes.com|access-date=2016-03-21|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308151008/https://www.forbes.com/sites/samanthasharf/2014/06/13/priceline-reserves-opentable-for-2-6-billion/}}</ref> 而Priceline集團也是 Group also owns Corporate Flights.

